76561198083818737,Recommended,263300,14118166,"Posted: 22 January, 2015",all,Spoken Normals,"Well I thought I had seen the limits of fighting games but boy was I wrong and I am so happy that I was!This game introduces a fast paises combat system with a wide veriaty of play styles that will suit different charaters such as toukaka who is a very fast charater darting across the screen landing rapid light hits, with a great design choice by the developers (I think anyway), each and every character has different play styles that requires you to think on your feet when challenging different characters.Gameplay is not the only thing that this game has going for it, the OST (Original Sound Track) has some just exilerating songs to not only go with the game but a copy of the OST is given with a purchus of the BlazBlue: Calamity Trigger so you can use it with other games and can even be downloaded to you audio listening device.The Graphics are somthing that I simple just love with dynamic backrounds and amazingly detailed character sprites this game allows for a fresh new experiance that is very different from other fighters like Street Fighter, Mortal Kombat, Guilty Gear, ETC.This is truely an amazing Japanese Fighter with the highest difficulty being HELL you know you are in for a challenge.Overall rateing  8.5/10"
